caption: A heavy stack of small metal cubes rests on a polished wooden floor, their sleek surfaces reflecting the warm tones of the wood. Suddenly, the stack of cubes begins to glide smoothly across the floor. The subtle sound of metal against wood accompanies its journey, creating a rhythmic pattern as it continues its path across the room.
